resources.string: A Technical and Practical Learning Club(or ATPLC) is a technical and practical club which aimed at providing practical learning experience and an all-round development to the tech-students. Initiated in 2020 from Motihari College of Engineering, Motihari Campus, through this club we aims at motivating students to learn proper set of skills apart from semester syllabus which is required to make them stand apart from mob. This club also helps students to sort out problems and confusion they are facing during learning any specific skill.Apart from that it also provide them a platform to show their existing skill and also help them to nurture it by competing themselves with other same skill occupying students.And overall these procedure help them in developing a proper stack of skill which will help them in placement or while working in organization. Apart from all these, this club also helps students to clear doubt related to their semester subjects by organizing discussion and doubt clearing classes. So,overall this club focus at helping a student in their all-round development to become fit for professional world.
